author: COMSOL
description: This example presents a homogenized numerical model of a corrugated sheet based on a unit cell, where numerically obtained equivalent stiffness matrices are compared with various analytical models. Two corrugation profiles, trapezoidal and round, are considered in this example.
label: corrugated_sheet.mph
name: root
